name: The Chiseling of the Rosseta Stone, and the Prophecy it Foretold
description: This is a combination piece containing elements of Collage, Digital Painting, AI, and Comic styling. I tried to leave lots of room for interpretation and enough space for your imagination to run wild. Question: Are we living in the most crucial time period on earth? Is it our fault, or simply the loosening of the strings holding our quilted dimension together? Where will we merge from here?
